### Advanced Styles Configuration

```js
const {
  Document,
  Paragraph,
  TextRun,
  HeadingLevel,
  AlignmentType,
  UnderlineType,
  ShadingType,
  BorderStyle,
  TabStopType,
  TabStopPosition,
  SpaceType,
  PageOrientation,
